    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban all cold-calling at residential properties",
        "additional_details": "People should not have put up with it.\r\n \r\nI am self-employed, we mainly fit kitchens and Bathrooms, I have never knocked on a door asking for work.We have however come across people who have fallen victim to this type of seller.\r\n \r\nWe need to put a stop to it.",
        "background": "Make it an offence to knock on doors touting for business. Some people adopting this type of sales tactic can be extremely persistent and intimidating.",
